<div class="foodies_1">
  
  <button class="btn btn-primary foodies_1_btn">Learn More</button>
</div>

<div class="container features">
  <br>
  <div class="row merchant_2_description">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-12 merchant_2_pic_1"></div>
    <div class="col-md-8 col-xs-12 merchant_2_text">
      <i class="fa fa-3x fa-search" aria-hidden="true"></i><span class="merchant_2_text_header">Restaurant Discovery</span>
      <hr>
      <p>Conveniently search for restaurants of your preference using various filters such as location, food type and waiting times</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row merchant_2_description">
    <div class="visible-xs-12 hidden-md hidden-lg col-xs-12 merchant_2_pic_2"></div>
    <div class="col-md-8 col-xs-12 merchant_2_text">
      <span><i class="fa fa-3x fa-hourglass-half" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><span class="merchant_2_text_header">Queue Remotely</span>
      <hr>
      <p>Wander around with a peace of mind while waiting for your table to be ready, as the restauranteur will send you push notifications minutes before your turn is up</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm col-md-4 merchant_2_pic_2"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="row merchant_2_description">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-12 merchant_2_pic_3"></div>
    <div class="col-md-8 col-xs-12 merchant_2_text">
      <i class="fa fa-3x fa-address-book" aria-hidden="true"></i><span class="merchant_2_text_header">Table Booking</span>
      <hr>
      <p>Place a table booking immediately after viewing reviews and menu and being satisfied with what the restaurant has got to offer</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row merchant_2_description">
    <div class="visible-xs-12 hidden-md hidden-lg col-xs-12 merchant_2_pic_4"></div>
    <div class="col-md-8 col-xs-12 merchant_2_text">
      <i class="fa fa-4x fa-mobile" aria-hidden="true"></i><span class="merchant_2_text_header">Chat Enquiries</span>
      <hr>
      <p>Message restaurant managers with our in-built chat function for enquiries, enabling a convenient a continuous conversation as you wish</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm col-md-4 merchant_2_pic_4"></div>
  </div>

  <br>
</div>

<div class="merchant_3">
  <p class="merchant_3_header">Drop your email with us to be first in the know when our service is ready</p>
  <br>
  <div class="merchant_3_form">

  <%= form_for @lead, url: lead_create_path(format: 'js'), remote: true, :method => 'post' do |form| %>

    <%= form.text_field :email, placeholder: "Your email...", type: 'text', pattern: "[a-z0-9._%+-]+@[a-z0-9.-]+\.[a-z]{2,3}$", class: 'merchant_3_form_input'  %>
    <span><%= form.button "Sign up for beta", class: "btn btn-primary merchant_3_form_btn", data: {target: "#myModal", toggle: "modal"}%></span>

  <% end %>

  </div>

  <div class="copyright">
    <h5>&copy; 2017 Potacto. All Rights Reserved.</h5>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="myModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
  <div class="modal-dialog">

    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
        <h4 class="modal-title">Sign Up for Beta</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <canvas height="0" class="canvas"></canvas>
        <p class="modal_text"></p>
        <div class="modal_form">
          <%= form_for :form_submit, url: lead_form_submit_path(format: 'js'), remote: true, :method => 'post' do |f| %>
          <%= f.text_field :name, placeholder: "Your First and Last Name...", class: "modal_form_input" %>
          <br>
          <br>
          <%= f.text_field :email, placeholder: "Email", class: "modal_form_input", id: "modal_input" %>
          <br>
          <br>
          <%= f.button "Submit", class: "btn btn-primary modal_form_btn" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
 
    </div>

  </div>
</div>